General.Name: Avrasya Petrol ve Turistik Tesisler Yatirimlar AS
General.Description: Avrasya Petrol ve Turistik Tesisler Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi operates tourism and oil facilities. The company purchases, sells, exports, and imports petroleum and petroleum products, fuel oil, diesel, and LPG; and engages in buying, selling, and leasing movable and real estate, machinery, and fixtures. The company was formerly known as Merkez B Tipi Menkul Kiymetler Yatirim Ortakligi AS and changed its name to Avrasya Petrol ve Turistik Tesisler Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi in January 2011. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
